# Project Overview

Personal portfolio and writing site at **jetsemrick.com**, statically exported to GitHub Pages.

## Stack

- Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v4 with `@tailwindcss/typography`
- Bun for package management and scripts
- Markdown posts in `content/posts/` (gray-matter + remark)

## Layout

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/app/` | Pages and routes |
| `src/components/` | Shared UI components |
| `src/lib/posts.ts` | Post loading and parsing |
| `src/lib/utils.ts` | `cn()`, `formatDate()` |
| `content/posts/` | Markdown blog posts |
| `public/` | Static assets, `CNAME` |

## Commands

```bash
bun install
bun run dev      # local dev
bun run lint     # eslint
bunx tsc --noEmit
bun run build    # static export to ./out
```

## Deployment

Push to `main` triggers `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`: lint → typecheck → build → GitHub Pages.

## Conventions

- Path alias: `@/` → `src/`
- Icons: Lucide React only
- `"use client"` only when hooks or browser APIs are required
- External links: `target="_blank"` + `rel="noopener noreferrer"`
